Now is the time to learn about COVID-19 vaccines, ask questions, and understand whether and when vaccination might be right for you.

COVID-19 Vaccine Availability in Utah, Idaho, and Nevada

COVID-19 vaccines are effective at protecting people from getting seriously ill, being hospitalized, and even dying. As with other diseases, you are protected best from COVID-19 when you stay up to date with COVID-19 vaccines.

Are You Up to Date?

You are up to date with your COVID-19 vaccines when you have received all doses in the primary series and all boosters recommended for you, when eligible. Vaccine recommendations are different depending on your age, the vaccine you first received, time since your last dose, and your whether you are immunocompromised.
